@{"Infinite Energy" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(30230,183) ZXAMPoke(30256,183)"}         30230,183:30256,183

                         Woah! What an AMAZING "Exclusive" game Sinclair User
                         scooped here! Just "Lightfarce" (the hidden game in
                         the 128K version of Zub), with a new frontend, a grating
                         tune, and changing the yellow to white!! Must have
                         taken Binary Design ages.. Well, they did write the
                         original game in an afternoon (they tell you in the
                         Zub version), so make of that what you will...

                         (Heavy on the sarcasm).

                         Rastan.
